file=AI & Agents/scout/operational/skill/scout-skill-routing.md · s—s:scout — Skill Routing (no identity layer — non-leader)=```\ncadence ─► ecosystem-scanning ─shortlist─► tool-evaluation-intake (tools) / marketplace-skill-scouting (skills) / forge (techniques) / edge (platforms)\n▲ checks first: adopt-reject-registry\nintake verdict ─► adopt-reject-registry (record) ─adopts─► relay (register + grants)\nbuild starts / PENDING note ─► marketplace-skill-scouting ─► present → STOP → operator approval → meta's standards\n```\n\nHandoffs out: relay (registration) \· aegis (security judgment) \· forge (technique candidates) \· edge (platform candidates) \· operator (every adoption approval) \· quinn (sandbox for trials).\nPrecedence: registry check > expiring verdicts > solicited searches > cadence scans.\n